metadata.name: high high
metadata.description:
My work begins with a scribble that reflects on the daily life of the worries and desires of the time.
I color my visualized mind with digital painting.


high high, 28 x 21.05 cm, 6614 x 4972 pixel 600dpi, digital painting, 2013
This is the first work that is the beginning of my current digital painting approach.
It was a drawing that I started with a free mind to forget my anxiety about my career.
but, the confusion of the time and the fear of the unknown future leaked into the image.
